<typeStatus id="54F5884A993D115CFB35FB70FB7FFACB" box="[1178,1228,1278,1301]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">type</typeStatus>
specimen indicates that Atoyac is in ‘‘Estado Veracruz’’; however the only Atoyac locality known to me is located in ‘‘Estado Guerrero’’.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
